      <description>Did anyone raise any corruption allegations against vaccine procurement during the Awami League years? No. Then what was the need to fix what was not broken? And this gentleman is now pontificating on the importance of following procedures and rules when his government exploited all loopholes in those procedures and rules to hand over Laldia terminal and bend over backwards to please the US and do as they please. We have 200+ innocent children dying for your supposed insistence on following procedures. Have some shame, show some remorse. Just keep quiet. PS. It’s incredible that he’s calling UNICEF Bangladesh liars.</description>
